# Portfolio Rules

Always read PORTFOLIO_SPEC.md before implementing features.

Follow the design language defined in PORTFOLIO_SPEC.md.

Never introduce new colors.

Never use gradients.

Never use glassmorphism.

Use monochrome design.

Use GSAP for scroll animations.

Use Framer Motion for component animations.

All content must come from the content folder.

Never hardcode project information.

Always create reusable components.

Maintain accessibility and SEO.

Optimize for Lighthouse score above 95.